      </div>
      <div class="hp-journey__visual">
        <div class="hp-journey__map">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 800 300" class="hp-journey__svg" id="journey-svg">
            <!-- Simplified HK→Canada flight arc -->
            <path class="hp-journey__arc" d="M 120,200 Q 400,20 680,180" fill="none" stroke="rgba(211,25,31,0.3)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/>
            <path class="hp-journey__arc-fill" d="M 120,200 Q 400,20 680,180" fill="none" stroke="#D3191F" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="1200" stroke-dashoffset="1200"/>
            <!-- HK dot -->
            <circle class="hp-journey__dot" cx="120" cy="200" r="6" fill="#D3191F"/>
            <text x="120" y="230" fill="#888" font-size="11" font-family="Oswald" text-anchor="middle" letter-spacing="0.1em">HONG KONG</text>
            <!-- Canada dot -->
            <circle class="hp-journey__dot" cx="680" cy="180" r="6" fill="#D3191F"/>
            <text x="680" y="210" fill="#888" font-size="11" font-family="Oswald" text-anchor="middle" letter-spacing="0.1em">CANADA</text>
            <!-- Plane -->
            <g class="hp-journey__plane" transform="translate(120,200)">
              <polygon points="0,-4 8,4 0,2 -8,4" fill="#D3191F" opacity="0.9"/>
            </g>
            <!-- Distance counter -->
            <text class="hp-journey__distance" x="400" y="100" fill="#D3191F" font-size="36" font-family="Oswald" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" letter-spacing="0.05em" opacity="0.8">7,654 km</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-journey__stats">
          <div class="hp-journey__stat" data-reveal>
            <span class="hp-journey__stat-num">7,654</span>
            <span class="hp-journey__stat-label">Kilometers</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hp-journey__stat" data-reveal>
            <span class="hp-journey__stat-num">12</span>
            <span class="hp-journey__stat-label">Hour Flight</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hp-journey__stat" data-reveal>
            <span class="hp-journey__stat-num">1</span>
            <span class="hp-journey__stat-label">Dream</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ====== RED LINE DIVIDER ====== -->
  <div class="hp-rink-divider">
    <div class="hp-rink-divider__line hp-rink-divider__line--red"></div>
    <div class="hp-rink-divider__puck"></div>
    <div class="hp-rink-divider__line hp-rink-divider__line--red"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ====== FAQ ====== -->
  <section class="hp-section hp-faq" id="faq">
    <div class="hp-container">
      <div class="hp-header-center">
        <div class="hp-label" data-reveal>Questions</div>
        <h2 class="hp-heading" data-reveal>Parents Ask</h2>
        <p class="hp-subtitle" data-reveal>The honest answers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hp-faq__list">
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>What if my kid is homesick?</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>We check in weekly. Group chat with all three mentors. We treat every player like our own. Your kid is never alone in Canada.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>What if the team isn't the right fit?</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>We evaluate before placement. We know the coaches. We've done this before. If something isn't working, we address it early.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>Do you guarantee placement?</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>No. We guarantee effort. We don't make promises we can't keep. But we've placed players because we do the work.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>How do I stay connected with my kid?</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>Weekly updates from us. Coach communication. WhatsApp group. You'll know what's happening every step of the way.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>How much does it cost?</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>It depends on the service. <a href="#contact">Contact us</a> for a conversation about your kid's needs and what makes sense.</p></div>
